|2 |  ├─TABLE FULL SCAN                |current_addr          |500     |24          |
|3 |  └─HASH JOIN                      |                      |275     |2216        |
|4 |    ├─SUBPLAN SCAN                 |dn                    |275     |1939        |
|5 |    │ └─HASH GROUP BY              |                      |275     |1938        |
|6 |    │   └─MERGE JOIN               |                      |275     |1794        |
|7 |    │     ├─TABLE FULL SCAN        |customer_address      |500     |24          |
|8 |    │     └─SORT                   |                      |287     |1718        |
|9 |    │       └─HASH JOIN            |                      |287     |1630        |
|10|    │         ├─TABLE FULL SCAN    |store                 |12      |3           |
|11|    │         └─HASH JOIN          |                      |301     |1591        |
|12|    │           ├─TABLE FULL SCAN  |household_demographics|200     |28          |
|13|    │           └─HASH JOIN        |                      |626     |1451        |
|14|    │             ├─TABLE FULL SCAN|date_dim              |46      |51          |
|15|    │             └─TABLE FULL SCAN|store_sales           |5000    |951         |
|16|    └─TABLE FULL SCAN              |customer              |1000    |66          |
=====================================================================================
